INSTALL:
-Copy the minifier directory and minifier.gedit-plugin file into your 
gedit plugins directory.

-Start or restart gedit

-Open the Preferences, and navigate to Plugins, check to enable Minifier plugin

USE:
-With your js or css file the active document go to Tools -> Minify JS or Minify CSS
-The minified file contents will be copied to your clipboard, paste the contents 
where desired
